Ariana Miyamoto was crowned Miss Japan last month . 
  She was born and raised in Japan and will represent her country at Miss Universe . 
  The 20-year-old says she was the only black girl in her class growing up . 
  Some critics have complained she is a mixed race 'hafu' and not Japanese enough . 
  Ariana grew up in Sasebo where her African-American father met her Japanese mother . 
  She says she has faced racial abuse growing up and was called a n****r by her peers . 
 